               <p>Second London Jury - before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1377. 
               <persName id="t18280703-29-defend323" type="defendantName">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MILLINGHAM
               <interp inst="t18280703-29-defend323" type="surname" value="MILLINGHAM"></interp>
